titles.title: Ascribe to the Lord oh mighty ones

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Ascribe to the Lord
Oh mighty ones
Ascribe to the Lord
Glory and strength

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Ascribe the Lord
the glory due His name
worship the Lord
In the beauty of His holiness

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
Bow down before Him
Love and adore Him
Come and sing praises to
Jesus our Lord
